creator: Cyclones
descriptionHtml:
THE GAME IS LINKS ANIMALS CLASSIC
Animal match game is a classic game from 2003. You must have played through the classic game of those years.


-HOW TO PLAY:
+ Match a pair of identical animals with up to three lines to clear them.
+ Eliminate all the animals in the game before the time runs out.
+ Whenever there are no more pairs to match, the animals will automatically reverse position.
+ When you can't find a matching pair, use a support item.

- FEATURES:
+ The game offline and easy to play!
+ Playable even when your phone does not have an internet connection.
+ Train your memory, observation, and hand manipulation.
+ Modern graphics, matching the latest trends! Beautiful shimmering effects, full of charm!
+ Compete with high scores with other players!
